lead_paragraph: Teenager Mitch Iles will shoot for Australia at the Rio de Janeiro Games following the disqualification of double Olympic champion Michael Diamond for drink-driving and firearms offences.

headline.print_headline: Shooter Iles Sets Sights on Rio After Diamond Dumped
